{"tid":1659560,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"每晚都係神探出末既時間","createTime":"2019-10-17T04:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T15:49:05.000Z","uid":64810,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9faea1a864c732a94c0d5999bad1b5922bee06d2","tid":1659560,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iq8oKyt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fiq8oKyt.png&h=ae835d19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n下一頁仲有幾個post都係講彥霖 9月初個種查案風又黎啦<br />\n<br />\n無人理黨鐵配合港警共自製宵禁，爛左執玻璃成個客戶服務部可以唔好足咁多日<br />\n<br />\n到左今日都無人貼1020既遊行文宣 最後自己落手貼<br />\n<br />\n請係地關注下行動啦 我真係好攰 廣傳上述既野<br />\n請繼續宣傳 岺子杰比人毆打同香港人人權受嚴重迫害<br />\n及煲大政府高官竟然叫市民唔好再追究721"},{"pid":"8710e08c2301da3ba8f6ae7b1abb8a18ed9d2a2a","tid":1659560,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:23:46.000Z","msg":"「突發」大量民陣1020九龍大遊行文宣流出<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1655703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1655703</a>"},{"pid":"2300080e0d96bbbe93b482986fcfe3b0f7503da9","tid":1659560,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:24:49.000Z","msg":"一陣實見到bot既回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd704473ea664d8c7bfc2dc1efcd44d88c9dde8","tid":1659560,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:25:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50c010881bb49f70f8fd3363779f2fc352cd4d72","tid":1659560,"uid":182406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:25:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc585e4c0667b581c25740f87c94bfa097be18fa","tid":1659560,"uid":64810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:25:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b52956b